{"tid":1469692,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無可能道歉。","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:10:12.000Z","uid":107060,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2828cdab0c170fa9ffe400348758fe478018fa","tid":1469692,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"見到好多人話今日行動綱領係道歉，我想講，<br />\n<br />\n無可能道歉。<br />\n<br />\n你一道歉，就証明你認為自己所做嘅事錯咗，只要有呢個念頭，對家就咬緊你唔放了。<br />\n<br />\n塞得機場就預咗係阻住人架啦，難道做呢啲行動之前，無諗清楚架咩？定係想又可以攞到抗爭光環，又唔願意接受現實，但又認為咁就會成功？<br />\n<br />\n人家政權開盡宣傳機器去對付我地，我地仲要比子彈對家射返我地？無可能呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n我地心中都要有一個覺悟，就係而家係戰爭狀態啊。而戰爭，就係用盡一切方法都要贏的一件事。<br />\n<br />\n即使做嘅事係會影響到人。<br />\n<br />\n五年前，同五年後，我都只得一個問題想問大家：大家到底係想贏，定係想做咗嘢就算？<br />\n<br />\n想贏嘅話，就係會令自己滿身泥濘啊。但就算係咁，都要挺起胸膛，行落去，<br />\n<br />\n咁先會贏啊！"},{"pid":"b5e8cbec9303e8a5d6ecbdf8cd408131f03a791f","tid":1469692,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b0821533d4a270490cb0db27bdb695094f0f5d8","tid":1469692,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5af99870b7572c22b9fa5e28a50c7fc1a9e89c6","tid":1469692,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a8ded0dd6e964594f2dd7ffb58c62068935ae898","tid":1469692,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503a6e6d3bd61e41286fe58a3e9f6b9505e2cfb0","tid":1469692,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n<br />\n機場和理非麻煩用下腦 道歉倒不如華御結<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解又要道歉？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bec80a0e898dea5057df1eefa0ba5da8477fd40c","tid":1469692,"uid":127751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bab9e23d7d349f26480bd51ae3ee19cd6c250aa","tid":1469692,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}